Final version chaged:

Hello guys this is my new release. Map is still in beta maybe there are bugs. If you found some plz report

Here video preview 
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L9SSfA7vqdU

Map Contains:

Pokemons
18 Traps
4 Minigames
1 epic Boss
48 Ct Spawns
3 T spawns
Afk killer
3 Secret special nades with secret things

and a fairness system:
there are shortcuts to the end of the level at choosen positions. If more than 3 Cts are playing,the 1. shortcut closes. If more than 7 Cts are playing, all shortcuts closes

This is made so that teams with 4 Cts have a chance to win because on other maps its impossible to beat a map with 3 or less Cts at beginning, resulting T giving free round that delayes the round because all have to run through the whole map
